About:
------
Customization for Vim 7

Installation:
-------------

1. Clone this repository into ~/.vim (~/vimfiles on Windows)
2. Link ~/.(g)vimrc to ~/(g)vimrc
   (On windows use 'fsutil hardlink create')
3. In ~/.vimrc run `git submodule update --init`
4. Make directory ~/.vim/autoload, and link ~/.vim/pathogen/autoload/pathogen.vim ~/autoload/pathogen.vim
   (Create hardlinks on Windows for this too)

Plugins:
--------
Install from git repository with `git submodule add <path> bundle/<plugin>`
Then commit when ready `git commit -m "Installed <plugin> as submodule"`
